{"word":"G3616 - οἰκοδεσποτέω - oikodespotéō - oy-kod-es-pot-eh'-o - Guide the house","slug":"G3616","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">οἰκοδεσποτέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>oikodespotéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>oy-kod-es-pot-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Guide the house"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>οἰκοδεσποτέω</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Oikodespoteo</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>oy-kod-es-pot-eh'-o</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> to be master (or head) of a house </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> to rule a household, manage family affairs </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G3617\">G3617</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 02:49,1 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Verb <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G3617\">G3617</a>; to <i>be</i> the <i>head of</i> (that is <i>rule</i>) <i>a</i> <b><i>family</i></b>: - guide the house. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2026\">G2026</a>, <a href=\"#/G2731\">G2731</a>, <a href=\"#/G2732\">G2732</a>, <a href=\"#/G2733\">G2733</a>, <a href=\"#/G3609\">G3609</a>, <a href=\"#/G3611\">G3611</a>, <a href=\"#/G3613\">G3613</a>, <a href=\"#/G3614\">G3614</a>, <a href=\"#/G3615\">G3615</a>, <a href=\"#/G3617\">G3617</a>, <a href=\"#/G3618\">G3618</a>, <a href=\"#/G3619\">G3619</a>, <a href=\"#/G3620\">G3620</a>, <a href=\"#/G3621\">G3621</a>, <a href=\"#/G3622\">G3622</a>, <a href=\"#/G3623\">G3623</a>, <a href=\"#/G3624\">G3624</a>, <a href=\"#/G4925\">G4925</a>"}]}